# Canonical organization and institution nodes reused across the bibliography graph.
#
# Use this file for publishers, documentation sites, conferences, and academic institutions that
# are referenced from works or references. Prefer one stable `org:<slug>` node per real entity and
# link to it from the other fragments instead of copying names and URLs inline. Reserve
# `schema:CollegeOrUniversity` for academic institutions; use `schema:Organization` for everything
# else.
@prefix schema: <https://schema.org/> .
@prefix dibs: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/vocab#> .
@prefix ref: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/ref/> .
@prefix person: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/person/> .
@prefix org: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/org/> .
@prefix work: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/work/> .
@prefix usage: <https://dibs.ravenhill.cl/bibliography/usage/> .

